      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do we need to update Android to pretend Alpha_8 is Gray?\n\n(Maybe not - we don\u0027t really know whether they truly mean Alpha_8 or Gray, and we did not support encoding Alpha_8 before, so they\u0027ll just not get to take advantage of this feature.)",
